.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
5 different games are played: backgammon, poker, go, billiard, domino
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person playing backgammon is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person playing domino##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person playing domino is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Game         | poker | domino  | billiard    | backgammon    | go        |

