City: hannover, edinburgh, london, new-york, prague
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, ship, skateboard, taxi
 1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person traveling to london is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the egyptian##2
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
 7. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the mexican is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is the turkish##1
10. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person traveling to london is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | photography | skydiving  | collecting | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish     | egyptian   | french     | mexican      |
