10. the fan of rock is on the left of the french##1
11. the fan of r&b is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
